title: WOW!! Look At Your New Home Today
posting_body: ['Welcome Home to Lakeview Heights', "They say home isn't a place, but a feeling.", "Located in the lovely little suburb of Lakewood, Colorado, Lakeview Heights Apartments' pet-friendly one and two bedroom apartments come with all the modern conveniences to help you create a space that's just right for you.", 'Plus, community perks like a resort-style pool make coming home a celebration of the everyday.', "All this and more surrounded by natural beauty that's truly breathtaking to behold.", 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'More unit details at:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 715 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Air Conditioning & Ceiling Fans', '- Spacious Floor Plans Designed For You', '- Vinyl, Wood-Style Flooring', '- Pet-Friendly Living - Dogs & Cats Welcome!', '- New Appliances', '- 1 & 2 Bedroom Floor Plans', '- Polished & Resurfaced Countertops', '- Modern, Open Living Area', 'Community Amenities', '- Close to the Light Rail', '- Ideal Location Near Lakeview Heights', '- Community Picnic Area With Pergola', '- BBQ & Picnic Area', '- Off Street Parking', '- Landscaped Grounds', '- Resort-Inspired Swimming Pool', '- Open Natural Spaces & Trail System', '- Onsite Laundry Facility', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet-Friendly Living - Dogs & Cats Welcome!', 'Breed Restrictions Apply.', 'Income Requirements:', 'Combined gross monthly income of 2.5x the rent amount.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Lakeview Heights', '10250 W Mississippi Ave, Lakewood, CO, 80226', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'q7emC91E']
